---
import Logo from '../components/Logo.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="JF Yardworks - A Maine Landscaping Company - About Us">
  <div class="about">
    <div class="about-text">
      <img src="/truck2.avif" alt="JF Landscaping plow truck" />
      <div style="padding: 24px;">
        <p>
          JF Yardworks is a family-owned, fully insured landscaping buisness centered in Gorham, Maine, specializing in residential and
          commercial property maintenance for our local communities. We provide year-round services to handle all four seasons that maine
          offers us.
        </p>

        <p>
          We believe in providing great customer service while getting the job done correctly and in a timely manner. We are fully licensed
          and insured with the state of Maine. Herb, the owner, comes with years of experience with snow removal and landscaping. You can
          rely on JF Yardworks to manicure your property into pristine condition and keep it that way year-round. Whether you just need
          weekly mowing or full-scale property maintenance - we're here for you! Give us a call today for a free estimate.
        </p>

        <p>
          <span class="text-gradient underline">Residential customers:</span> along with mowing and plowing we offer many services for all of
          your personal property maintenance needs. Maybe this is the year you give your garden beds a facelift; we offer and install a variety
          of high-quality mulch bedding. Have a junk pile sitting around you've been meaning to ditch/recycle? Call us for a dump haul. Whatever
          your property cleanup needs may be, we are here and eager to get the job done!
        </p>

        <p>
          <span class="text-gradient underline">Commercial customers:</span> when running a business your focus and energy is best spent running
          your day-to-day operation. You don't have time to worry about the lawn and landscaping needs, snow removal, or keeping employees safe
          with clear pathways to and from your facility - leave that to JF Yardworks! We will keep your buisness property looking great with
          safe passage all year.
        </p>

        <p>
          At JF Yardworks we pride ourselves in a job well done. Being a family business, we enjoy meeting new people and forming valuable
          relationships within our community that last a lifetime. We strive to leave a positive, lasting impression with each of our
          clients and won't hesitate to go above and beyond to make your property care wishes come true.
        </p>
        <div class="service-areas">
          <p>
            Service areas include:
            <ul>
              <li>Gorham</li>
              <li>South Windham</li>
              <li>Westbrook</li>
              <li>Portland</li>
              <li>Scarborough</li>
              <li>Saco</li>
              <li>South Buxton</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
  $breakpoint: 1024px;
  .about {
    height: 100%;
    background-image: linear-gradient(120deg, #fdfbfb 0%, #ebedee 100%);

    padding: var(--gap);

    img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border-radius: 8px 0 0 8px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }
  }

  .underline {
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .about-text {
    max-width: 1440px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: white;

    line-height: 1.8em;
    color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
    border-radius: 2px;
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow:
      0 3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07),
      0 3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    height: fit-content;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 5fr 7fr;

    @media screen and (max-width: $breakpoint) {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;

      img {
        max-height: 250px;
      }
    }

    p:first-child {
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }
  }

  .back-home-container {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .service-areas {
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  a {
    color: rgb(var(--accent));
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
